title: Week 3 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp play ‘Start, Bench, Cut’ with the biggest names for Week 3, including how you should manage stars like Derrick Henry and Tom Brady. Plus, Liz Loza joins to give us what QB’s need to be in your lineup.
